You are a robot with a fixed base and a single gripper that can pick up and place objects into containers.

There are two movable objects on the table: apple (a fruit), yellow-cube (a cube).

There are also two containers available: bowl1 (a bowl), box1 (a cardboard box).

Both the apple and the yellow cube are currently resting on the table, and your gripper is empty.

Your task is to place the apple into the bowl and place the yellow cube into the cardboard box.